{
  "texts": [
    "The CALTECH 256 and MIT scene datasets demonstrated that the proposed FC-GPHOG image descriptor provides promising results in the realm of object and scene image categorization.",
    "When an inappropriate PCA space is used, the model overfits.",
    "Similarly, for image segmentation and grouping, [28] employed Fuzzy C-means, as well as the Gabor Filter, Gray Low Covariance Matrix (GLCM), and Color histogram.",
    "To learn and identify satellite images, the Support Vector Machine (SVM) was utilised.",
    "The researchers classified components acquired from satellite images as desert, mountain, residential, river, and woodlands in their method."
  ]
}